{"tid":1321290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（緊急）發夢者的Telegram及WhatsApp要做多樣野防止被hack","createTime":"2019-07-15T15:32:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T16:45:30.000Z","uid":266172,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"63faff6039819429068fd8778f411f6ccdf628ff","tid":1321290,"uid":266172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:32:08.000Z","msg":"除左大家已知的之外，岩岩外國人發現左個新的vulnerability，要做下面2件事防止被hack。<br />\n<br />\n係WhatsApp<br />\nSettings&gt;Chats&gt;Media Visibility 要turn off<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dJA1Dxj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdJA1Dxj.jpg&h=983e5640&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n係telegram <br />\nSettings&gt;Chat Settings&gt;Save to Gallery要turn off<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UYD6PEt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUYD6PEt.jpg&h=8eb87e0b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔該幫頂，有玩telegram的幫手傳開, thanks."},{"pid":"474426bbf6bc8760755094bc913e6a93f7082181","tid":1321290,"uid":99243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:35:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ea41df7218e82678ecb50e10bf1cd04c2d839c0","tid":1321290,"uid":266172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:35:57.000Z","msg":"頂"},{"pid":"cba7a7926c008c84752114522918aaedec009297","tid":1321290,"uid":266172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:38:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a7b1fc0756dd37fb8bc420f808516fb2b7b4bd2","tid":1321290,"uid":49128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:39:09.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"4689a9ba6beace57c7cca8d7d863d69ee1975438","tid":1321290,"uid":266172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T15:43:03.000Z","msg":"唔該幫手share去telegram。"},{"pid":"1c71506ab3af11169a839bdc44ec417c22a60417","tid":1321290,"uid":266172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:00:20